  - body: "[Packet 6](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-6)"

"War Domain: War Priest":
  title: "War Domain Level 3: War Priest"
  desc: "Your training with weapons allows you to use the Mastery property of one kind of Simple or Martial weapon with which you have proficiency. Whenever you finish a Long Rest, you can change the kind of weapon you chose to another eligible kind.\n\nIn addition, you can make one weapon attack as a Bonus Action. You can use this Bonus Action a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a Short Rest or Long Rest."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 6](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-6)"

"War Domain: Guided Strike":
  title: "War Domain Level 3: Guided Strike"
  desc: "When you or a creature within 30 feet of you misses with an attack roll, you can use your Reaction to expend one use of your Channel Divinity and give that roll a +10 bonus, potentially causing it to hit."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 6](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-6)"

"War Domain: War God's Blessing":
  title: "War Domain Level 6: War God's Blessing"
  desc: "Whenever you cast _Shield of Faith_ on another creature, the spell also affects you.\n\nIn addition, you can cast the spell once without expending a spell slot, and you regain the ability to do so when you finish a Short Rest or Long Rest."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 6](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-6)"

"War Domain: Avatar of Battle":
  title: "War Domain Level 17: Avatar of Battle"
  desc: "You gain resistance to Bludgeoning, Piercing, and Slashing damage."
  fields:
  - body: "[Packet 6](https://www.dndbeyond.com/sources/ua/ph-playtest-6)"
